title: Supercars.Exposed-Speed2008-Maserati-Miami-Kanaan
description: SuperCars Exposed, Speed Channel (US) 2008, Hosted by Tanner Foust, 22 mins.  Tanner visits Miami&#039;s Lamborghini dealer and sees the customization options available.  Includes a Gallardo that has been creatively "tattooed" by an artist using only a Sharpie pen.  Tanner also checks out C.E.C. and the customization options they offer.  Plus he talks with race car driver Tony Kanaan about his customized cars -- Porsche 911, Porsche Cayenne, Mercedes CLK63 AMG.  Then there&#039;s a visit to the Maserati collection at the Riverside Automotive Museum in California, which includes a test drive of the Maserati MC12.  MP4 file, H264 codec, 640x480, captured from digital SDTV.  More episodes to come from tallearthling.
